data.description: Discover the epitome of luxury living in this spacious four-bedroom three bathroom home located in a prestigious community in NW Albuquerque!  The two separate living areas provide ample space for relaxation and socializing.  The kitchen provides an array of upscale amenities like upgraded appliances and granite counter tops.The main bedroom is a private retreat, boasting a generously-sized bedroom and opulent bathroom.The main bathroom features a garden tub, dual sinks, a make-up counter, and a separate shower. Three additional well-appointed bedrooms provide versatility and comfort, while the large backyard with a swimming pool and a covered patio is perfect for outdoor dining and entertainment. The neighborhood is within walking distance to grocery shopping and more!
